---
title: Spinach & Feta-Stuffed Chicken with Kumara Wedges & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Moist, succulent chicken is the perfect shell for this spinach and feta mixture. It’s akin to a chicken Kiev, but has more veggies and is far more delicious. It's classic comfort food, enjoyed from the comfort of your own home.
